  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디지털 소량 생산은</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-080d5cfa-1e87-4aa7-8114-ea169d08da70\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223914521724/000.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6f9f836f-6043-433c-b870-c47cc35746b2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bdb5a116-6636-4246-8e3a-cb2a5958a78e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b96241b5-ed80-4bd0-887d-340fc47c5c27\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9824a2ef-5158-456e-befd-59dbf9d18fc1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5db27dd6-725e-4b65-a477-3539641dc0e7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니 사이트의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-36472091-761b-4f41-b3f1-3443b0abfb9d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8cf713ca-af2e-4f7f-aa4a-4458b5b1cba5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">포트폴리오를 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7b5154ed-3df9-41d4-a5ae-5e673ace0aa9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-332e168f-e618-4962-a8b6-aa0a0984488a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://cookthedesign.co.kr/\" target=\"_blank\">https://(주)파파스컴퍼니.co.kr/</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c89bb15b-9a3f-4fbd-a6f7-08351073ce4b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223914521724/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">증정용 택에 대해서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">엠플이나 샘플을 소중한 사람에게 증정하거나 선물하려고 할 때는 디지털 커팅을 이용하여 제작하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7e16511a-8b49-471e-be6f-f2d3c502169b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-46183ba5-9cd3-4d2b-92a7-d799d72883a3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aed6cb5e-a690-4247-acac-cb9335a543d7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ace3e8fc-2c0c-4f64-8fe1-c277162ed5a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">엠플이나 샘플이 작거나 소량 사이즈일 때 끼워서 전달할 수 있도록 모양을 만들어 제작할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ec926702-9680-4d98-a195-46ee97070ef9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d3f9f9ae-cbe5-45a0-9a14-795fd884dcad\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-45fe0fb1-14fa-4d2b-bdc3-a7f2a6a22450\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223914521724/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9a1b3272-533f-4f27-ad77-974566be3b26\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dc15ab14-0c36-410b-ba4e-da71a458e8ca\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e4b393bf-fedf-43ca-8b90-aea27a74c48b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 이미지는 검은색이 커팅 되어 끼울 수 있는 모양을 만듭니다. 빨간색은 접히는 누름(오시)선입니다. 엠플의 끼우는 높이가 접혔을 때 사이즈일겁니다. 정확하게 제작을 하기 위해서는 반드시 샘플을 받아서 제작하시기를 추천드립니다. 이 높이가 맞지 않는다면 헐겁거나 끼워지지 않을 수 있으니 주의하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a2326a1f-8ef7-470d-9c3b-b50757785619\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-80a503e7-82ec-456b-91cd-2f1c7cb5b108\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-fd70e488-8786-4d4a-9f5b-eeb1e20845bb\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223914521724/003.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223914521724/004.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223914521724/005.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223914521724/006.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7aff8d40-0c5e-448a-9ccd-69fc540ba389\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-77c6ed5e-30ab-49bb-9ae2-167bc8bb6247\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-f1915664-ee06-4e1c-becc-a29d3ee4dc57\" style=\"\">제작 사양</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-448823ea-5dc9-4267-b8c2-04701c03e8c0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b7ba1514-3079-402c-b2db-8c1fea288aef\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-881eadf6-7df9-4403-a9f0-ba065c0b585a\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3150ecd3-6db2-4131-829c-ec0fe6dc4f01\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b63c9404-80e6-4c25-a42e-b0a5ff6434ca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이는 정말 자유롭습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d48c0768-2a72-461e-b88b-773f432bb6d6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:678px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223914521724/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-afa4f42c-f8ab-45a8-88bc-0faa02b60270\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-61de4c76-41de-4bec-9465-3d295b518dcc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f1f7a8db-b9be-4459-bba7-bffc94710336\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">본 이미지의 종이는 띤또레또 250g 순백색입니다. 띤또레또의 특징은 약간의 무결 무늬가 형성되어 있다는 겁니다. 물론 이런 물결무늬는 인쇄 시 방해될 수 있습니다. 방해라는 것은 진한 바탕색을 인쇄하고 싶다면 가급적 피하셔야 할 겁니다. 띤또레또나 휘라레 종이류는 진한 바탕색으로는 처리하지 않는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-32dd127a-c6a5-4cc6-9360-62b25c0887fc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-551f0ae2-a808-42cc-9484-d8f99ecbe069\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-be0750c2-e7e7-4ecd-bee0-864f36137adb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-70f235a4-1719-4276-81b3-1e355efa4833\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만약 바탕색이 있다면 띤또레또보다는 매끈한 매트 종이류가 좋습니다. 추천 종이는 인바이런먼트지나 슈퍼파인으로 제작하시기를 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-425174ed-61df-44db-88c1-54486382318f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4b272613-1bda-478c-901f-2f75c47aa657\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e7d842fc-a5a7-47a7-b51f-5c0927437f26\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fac28e6f-981b-494b-8923-1f50701888ee\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">여기서 중요한 것은 최소한 250g 이상의 종이를 준비하세요. 그 이하의 종이는 얇아서 후들거릴 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-21552d45-5501-4638-8c4a-10457464423b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2ce497d1-ad5f-40d9-ae83-455d51183af5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b166f62d-8053-4d28-9aeb-0837ea4c7ce1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d7bf2868-ca05-449d-b316-d914d933bd06\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>추천 종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7ce4abc4-6ed6-4209-bec8-790b3ed9c0e9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b675fd6d-0c84-4c95-9718-90a699647ffe\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>띤또레또</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eaeda913-cf44-4bd4-be3a-c213d200b3b0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 무늬 결의 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-44258011-fd99-45b1-ba4e-798b5121dfdb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f17af03e-81b4-4a6c-a4b2-38b4f9baabd6\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>아트지/스노우지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d4accac8-b077-4c30-92a2-39a0d024c817\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 가장 일반적인 종이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-277aac13-fe5f-4233-99a2-b0bc1dd40e43\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-14c57eb4-74cb-455a-acc0-06901f6b5b70\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>스타드림</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ea460cd9-c483-435c-97d4-de4872115b0f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 펄지처럼 독특한 것을 원하는 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1bacc2dc-4411-498b-a4c4-67b370533540\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-75780dd9-0aec-47dc-9a2e-939bf1c5b72b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>아르떼/반누브</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8145a1ad-a721-434b-adcd-f98af3af81ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 일반 고급지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6c30d0ff-c3d1-4198-a13d-78f096d300bc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e885d6c3-5bc8-4cb5-b733-8b25df03f8c7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>흑기사 외</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ccd0f118-e9e5-4c4f-979d-ce0d63279cb9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 색상이 들어간 종이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-25fe948a-33c3-4264-b253-82f5c37ac866\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dd2a8476-fbdd-4b17-b4ad-00f110c39b44\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-96b5bda3-ec12-43b0-bb25-d1285da241dd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5dd021ff-564a-4ed6-901f-0db7a4291190\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>사이즈</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-effd9259-3cbe-402b-88dd-53e5bc805117\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1ddbee31-0ce9-421b-9d60-2cc02bfc85c1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사이즈는 엠플 크기에 좌우됩니다. 엠플의 높이가 정해지면 끼우는 자리와 공간을 설정하여 도면을 그리게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-86df2556-7a41-4af1-bcfa-a4f7f3792d0d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:630px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223914521724/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3282e30b-441e-400a-8bfe-d97acdbf9032\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8d19fa77-894b-4970-9226-f317ef1610a8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-186eff80-950d-4673-8587-d42b7491b551\" style=\"color:#555555;\">높이는 11mm입니다. 이 공간이 엠플이 끼워지는 부분입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-246ca9e7-960a-42a3-ba4e-4613d41b6cd4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223914521724/009.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6354ad2a-9440-4f70-9e2b-e2877eca9348\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ee97e44c-455a-41d3-a373-e26291040038\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-43adc5d6-7603-4001-9ce8-cecac5bd8189\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 이미지는 샘플로 제작한 것입니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 본 작업 전에 샘플을 보내주시면 디지털로 샘플을 제작하고 작업에 들어갈 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d2c67384-2563-4dfa-92b0-2e0a0ea52180\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5bdd1636-bb24-4484-a137-2027dd41553c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cb3e96e3-dc65-4c5f-82b0-30a95d7e2e7a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b925b81a-4f5e-4c78-9537-7220a34d3402\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>기본 모양</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-db1aa120-ba80-4ba0-a9b3-7f6758e4609e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-36f99c6b-3512-48d1-8b78-97bfa6acbb6a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">중간에 엠플이 끼워지는 공간이 필요</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-24c2dc58-fe2c-48f4-8eb2-3e6525560df3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:401px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223914521724/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bd60a799-5162-4ace-a523-906b8382dd82\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cd5f42cb-48f9-4872-a5ff-1cdc3b0fc14f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cdf924f7-db1f-4729-a9ef-1f051232f968\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-82202461-7f5d-43f1-8b8a-bdc06cffd95c\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e3aa2ede-40f9-4de7-abcd-d1219d7114a5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0bd62de6-7adc-4f8e-b7bd-77fe27b9950f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄는 양면 컬러 인쇄가 기본입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-87628874-94a2-44cd-a5ed-ef5dbcdab6fe\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c3a59fcc-19af-4626-aeaa-e7739cbc598a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수량이 많은 경우는 별색인쇄도 가능합니다. 하지만 소량의 경우는 단가가 많이 증가되기 때문에 별색인쇄가 어렵습니다. 디지털 인쇄의 별색은 제한 사항이 발생됩니다. 최소한 수량이 몇 천 개 이상 주문 시에 별색이 진행되면 단가를 맞출 수 있다고 보시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0d5d9411-8090-4bed-aa89-fb554c6bd91a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8b1c977f-1c51-4d1b-8d14-202a07c9815a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3e03b0eb-0883-402e-80d2-db98012fea5f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-279baacd-7202-4228-9dc4-4e11db7f4a66\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">엠플용 디자인은 위에서 이야기 한 것처럼 바탕색을 진하게 깔지 않습니다. 특별한 생상이 바탕에 깔리고 싶으시면 색지 종이를 선택하시는 것이 유리합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b27515d3-3c3b-4f53-b10c-be8cf7efa42f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa6b74f0-6ccd-44a3-b49f-2b365084a5f8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-747c5554-050b-4be2-8fe5-235b1756d553\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7aa3fd05-e6d5-4002-9a3f-ce9c709d486b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 부분은 별도로 문의하시면 친절하게 안내드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-21e76df6-6bf2-46f2-8bee-88eb4051eb52\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7624ab8d-f135-4369-9839-b8f207905658\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-07faf772-f149-4d3c-9281-619a2aef6273\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-660c300d-4cea-4f7b-8de7-9e57b677ebfc\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>후공정</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eed09eda-83a2-4477-af8d-46fed60d7bae\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2b7c6e18-5e92-4ff0-b96f-740bdce75586\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털 커팅이 기본입니다. 디지털 커팅은 쉽게 되는 부분이지만 오시나 커팅 부분은 조금은 조심해야 합니다. 오시를 넣거나 커팅이 위 이미지처럼 겹치게 되면 커팅이 에러가 나거나 오시가 삐져나올 수 있습니다. 아직까지는 디지털 커팅이 100% 완벽하게 구현이 안 될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8e135faf-8e0d-4f9b-83f4-40a142fa08ff\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-882d4cf8-d872-44d5-96a5-d24896ceb4ad\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6d6c3704-6dd6-4c3e-92c1-601d4ddb4aa0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-99ce9f58-17b2-4f97-92fb-92df1d2b4451\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 경우 대량으로 목형 + 도무송(톰슨)작업을 하시면 좋습니다. 다만 수량이 적을 경우 단가적으로 손해가 발생하므로 반드시 (주)파파스컴퍼니과 상의하여 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d432f41f-b1cc-4ccb-84df-06df9f451f1f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b25e488a-aca3-48a0-827e-bd88e06c9f2e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-86818f03-be3f-4b67-a957-9ae7b7ea4f23\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-49ea669f-6e35-49bb-9575-72785156d406\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이외의 후공정은 박인쇄나 형압등이 가능합니다. 하지만 디지털 소량시에는 제약사항이 발생될 수 있으므로 주의하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b3208d7f-4921-45ff-8d7c-6d4d64961d93\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4982d72c-8730-4c22-a485-467aadd313e0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-540b79d0-4c93-4472-804a-e2cd1568c042\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6a314662-e28c-4828-9f59-fd09f464131e\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>기본 수량</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aad10b62-562f-4b18-a117-f3370e7e6d1b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-adcc6c5a-d645-4c10-8761-581edc834986\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털 주문 시에는 1장부터 가능합니다. 보통의 경우 200개 정도를 기준으로 디지털 주문이 가능합니다. 그 정도 내외의 수량이 넘어가면 오프셋으로 진행하는 것이 퀄리티나 단가적으로 이득이 될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5ddf2746-ba30-457c-8e62-67b16f073719\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-afaf9436-f971-4c45-b042-215243c01f01\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-960ccbcb-d756-4a3a-b550-2e94faf49db5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-71363fbf-5bab-4784-87db-ff6f84d2102a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디지털 수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1b45ae99-1e04-4d85-a60d-18bcb9625e38\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 1개에서 200개 내외까지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2e2e2623-1161-4ae3-a19b-7ad9464c3c84\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4ae9a651-4b79-49d0-b0e4-6a054aa21b5a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>오프셋 수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-db88ec74-e0da-473e-a2c9-2847d767c9e7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 200개부터 ~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-57fc2d1c-b475-412d-8fd0-5067f6486f4c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fc49a85e-e77b-4211-b0c8-0f5147e3aa31\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1a5fb1a9-29c7-4910-be84-29a3d98ebad6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a25a7226-49a9-45fc-a138-1222d766cfea\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만약 200개 300개 정도면 사이즈나 후공정에 따라 디지털과 오프셋의 단가를 비교하여 제안 드립니다. 만약 이 정도 수량이라면 100개를 디지털로 주문하시거나 500개를 오프셋으로 발주하는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-13b1a5a2-5360-4c78-ab65-9be61a7e3e29\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-659aff05-cd96-4273-abbb-a24aa4e399aa\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-89386b95-3d4f-4677-95f6-07bfb504f6d1\" style=\"\">제작일지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cf429151-8008-4cc3-bc46-64076a3f3ed6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:677px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223914521724/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-32bdc349-a27d-4bd9-b8a8-4d0cc6bddebd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:759px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223914521724/012.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3dfd3802-9b75-474a-a2cd-0c7eb4c0ab98\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4870f333-81ac-40fe-acf1-ad7bca8ea094\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-06f7466f-1857-40dd-82a6-403945929c5f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 데이터 검증을 꼼꼼히 해드리는 것으로 유명합니다. 사고 방지를 위해 많은 데이터 주문보다는 받은 데이터를 꼼꼼하게 체크해서 제작해 드리고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-89346bb8-dd13-4129-961d-469127185fd1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f3d51e29-744a-4f51-8c51-a3e41c9f3f62\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0ee605d3-b816-4995-b0e3-019a209bdafe\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f3e587dc-7dd5-4546-b4af-3a52a7726c7b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니이 진행하는 과정에서의 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-70bb655a-464a-49fc-a3da-1a168c040bd7\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>강점</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a88316ad-f543-4ced-b399-fc3708904a0b\" style=\"color:#54b800;\">​</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a39dd45f-a733-48f8-85e3-696e400607c3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-30ef6ab9-4d72-47aa-83db-f50162886835\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b89bca04-91e8-43d8-a40e-f8d5665ea15c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>데이터 검증을 꼼꼼히 점검</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8cfc2d3b-19f5-41ba-8c63-66fcaaa344c6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">해 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b80710d9-b947-4c0f-8d55-eb2551d6b5a1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0d241967-a43d-4e3b-be0f-2d86d8de1948\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>고객님의 납기를 가장 소중하게</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c6f9db68-6649-4b2f-8674-ec39b4e55e0b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 생각합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d5a969e3-b5a3-4fed-9abf-094dbdfc33a8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7ae3c1a5-a358-43c1-92e9-741c6262e09e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>퀄리티에 최선</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24401353-9411-472f-97bd-c0cb6b00b183\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을 다합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b0e32d34-1771-482b-adb0-978c7a3e736a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanu